{"tid":1856092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大逆轉！越南解禁「允許台灣航班入境」","createTime":"2020-02-01T12:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T09:40:50.000Z","uid":254183,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2412d3a8d151a6854d692299583995940da26231","tid":1856092,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"越南今日宣佈禁止中港澳台航班入境，導致星宇航空飛往峴港航班只好滑回機坪，長榮航班更是原機返台。不過剛剛越捷航空台灣總代理於臉書發布消息指出，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「越南民航局已經宣佈解禁台灣」</span></strong>，桃機公司表示，確實公告取消，詳細狀況還需進一步了解。<br />\n<br />\n桃機航務處長陳志嘉表示，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">禁行公告已取消台灣，僅保留中港澳</span></strong>，詳細狀況正進一步查證中。越捷航空則表示，即刻起航班一切順利運作。<br />\n<br />\n長榮及立榮航空接獲越南通知，接受台灣飛往越南之班機，今晚立榮航空B7-29將會維持飛航，但將延遲至23:00起飛，長榮與立榮航空明日以後往返越南之航班則均維持正常起降。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b226e8e5b4de63665dea19ea74f4dea501c387","tid":1856092,"uid":58841,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:29:45.000Z","msg":"支共口交部又要發癲了"},{"pid":"26a222a26896eaf9ab530fca8e49a0c5dd32bdd2","tid":1856092,"uid":129309,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:38:55.000Z","msg":"咁重好，強調返台灣is not china"},{"pid":"5bebd04c6bf5d476ec76eeef0f135b6999659e61","tid":1856092,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:39:59.000Z","msg":"口交部：越南不厚道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6ef833179bf5cdc3c64becf993382a14579db7","tid":1856092,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"台灣好波"},{"pid":"a468a3ff43446e61c0499930a73eac215f45c7e6","tid":1856092,"uid":324701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"越南真係好憎中共XD"},{"pid":"0d47d82dbb93a83f4fc538553f410de068886885","tid":1856092,"uid":254